General.Name: Nivika Fastigheter AB Series B
General.Description: Nivika Fastigheter AB (publ), a real estate company, acquires, develops, refines, and manages residential and commercial properties in Sweden. Its property portfolio consists of 130 properties, which include office and warehouse, apartment, industrial, and housing. Nivika Fastigheter AB (publ) was founded in 2000 and is headquartered in Värnamo, Sweden.
